sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Player as Player (Browser)
  participant MSAL as MSAL.js / Entra ID
  participant Client as Blazor WASM Client
  participant API as PoFace API (App Service)
  participant Vision as Google Cloud Vision
  participant Blob as Azure Blob Storage
  participant Table as Azure Table Storage

  note over Player,MSAL: ── AUTHENTICATION (Optional) ──
  Player->>+MSAL: Click "Login"
  MSAL-->>-Player: Redirect → Entra ID login page
  Player->>+MSAL: Credentials submitted
  MSAL-->>-Client: OIDC redirect with ID token + access token
  Client->>Client: Store token; OptionalAccessTokenHandler attaches on requests

  note over Player,Table: ── GAME SESSION START ──
  Player->>+Client: Click "Start Game"
  Client->>+API: POST /api/sessions  [Bearer token optional]
  API->>+Table: Insert GameSessionEntity (Incomplete)
  Table-->>-API: OK
  API-->>-Client: { sessionId, rounds[5 emotions] }
  Client-->>-Player: Show Round 1 — Target: Happiness 😄

  note over Player,Table: ── ROUND LOOP (×5) ──
  loop For each round 1–5
    Player->>+Client: Webcam frame captured (countdown → shutter)
    Client->>Client: GameOrchestrator FSM: Capturing → Analyzing
    Client->>+API: POST /api/sessions/{id}/rounds/{n}/score  (JPEG, max 500 KB)
    API->>+Vision: Annotate image — FaceDetection features
    Vision-->>-API: FaceAnnotation (Joy/Anger/Surprise/Sorrow/Fear likelihoods + headpose)
    API->>API: HeadPoseValidator (|yaw|≤20°, |pitch|≤20°)
    API->>API: Score = confidence → 0–10 (clamped)
    API->>+Blob: PutBlob poface-captures/{sessionId}_{round}.jpg
    Blob-->>-API: Blob URL
    API->>+Table: Insert RoundCaptureEntity
    Table-->>-API: OK
    API-->>-Client: { score, emotion, confidence, imageUrl }
    Client-->>-Player: ScoreReveal overlay (2 s)
  end

  note over Player,Table: ── SESSION COMPLETE ──
  Client->>+API: POST /api/sessions/{id}/complete
  API->>+Table: Read 5 RoundCaptureEntities → sum TotalScore
  Table-->>-API: Round data
  API->>API: IsPersonalBest? Compare LeaderboardEntity
  API->>+Table: Update GameSessionEntity (IsCompleted, TotalScore, IsPersonalBest)
  Table-->>-API: OK
  opt Authenticated + IsPersonalBest
    API->>+Table: Upsert LeaderboardEntity (Year partition)
    Table-->>-API: OK
  end
  API-->>-Client: { totalScore, isPersonalBest, recapUrl }
  Client-->>-Player: Game Over screen — score + recap link

  note over Player,Table: ── RECAP VIEW ──
  Player->>+Client: Open /recap/{sessionId}
  Client->>+API: GET /api/recap/{sessionId}
  API->>+Table: Query RoundCaptureEntities by sessionId
  Table-->>-API: 5 round entities
  API-->>-Client: { rounds[{ score, imageUrl, emotion }], totalScore }
  Client-->>-Player: Round gallery with images and scores
